      "text": "API server\n(remote-profile/server)\nExpress :4050\nPersistence: data/store.json\n\nPublic (peripheral / no login):\n• GET /api/profiles — catalog\n• GET /api/profiles/:profileId/latest\n  → { profile: BleProfile JSON }\n\nAdmin: full version rows, drafts, publish",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API server\n(remote-profile/server)\nExpress :4050\nPersistence: data/store.json\n\nPublic (peripheral / no login):\n• GET /api/profiles — catalog\n• GET /api/profiles/:profileId/latest\n  → { profile: BleProfile JSON }\n\nAdmin: full version rows, drafts, publish",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a6"
    },
