      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "peripheral-app (React Native)\n\nUI: Profile source → Remote\n• Fetch remote profiles (catalog)\n• User selects a row\n• GET …/latest → JSON document\n\nPipeline:\napplyValueGenerators → ProfileEngine\n→ native rn-ble-peripheral module\n(advertising + GATT like local JSON)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "peripheral-app (React Native)\n\nUI: Profile source → Remote\n• Fetch remote profiles (catalog)\n• User selects a row\n• GET …/latest → JSON document\n\nPipeline:\napplyValueGenerators → ProfileEngine\n→ native rn-ble-peripheral module\n(advertising + GATT like local JSON)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a8"
    },
